The '''International Network for Quality Assurance Agencies''' '''in Higher Education''' ('''INQAAHE''') is an International Quality Assurance body that works closely with National Accreditation bodies ([[CHEA]] in USA, [[ENQA]] in Europe) and academicians to control educational quality in around 140 countries. Established in 1991.

